<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>According to <a href="http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec10.html#sec10.3.7">RFC 2616</a>,</p>

<p>{quote}
The 306 status code was used in a previous version of the specification, is no longer used, and the code is reserved.
{quote}</p>

<p>If Redirector is HTTP/1.1-compliant (and I think it should be... HTTP/1.1 has been a standard for almost nine years and is universally implemented), then it should observe this restriction.</p>

